{"id":265617,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/【异闻观止】湖南日报-领导自掏腰包填肚子/","date":"2012-11-28T06:56:21Z","modified":"2012-11-28T06:56:24Z","title":"【异闻观止】湖南日报 | 领导自掏腰包填肚子","content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e6%b9%96%e5%8d%97%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5-%e9%a2%86%e5%af%bc%e8%87%aa%e6%8e%8f%e8%85%b0%e5%8c%85%e5%a1%ab%e8%82%9a%e5%ad%90/zitaoyaobao/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-265618\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-265618\" title=\"zitaoyaobao\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/11/zitaoyaobao.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/11/zitaoyaobao.jpg 1015w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/11/zitaoyaobao-300x179.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/11/zitaoyaobao-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1015px) 100vw, 1015px\" /></a></p>\n<p>11月22日，娄底市和新化县的部分领导干部来到新化县水车镇，与水车、文田、奉家3个乡镇新当选的县人大代表座谈。水车镇人民政府没有给参加会议的人员发香烟，也没有招待用餐，与会人员自掏腰包填肚子，博得群众一片喝彩声。</p>\n<p>来源：<a href=\"http://epaper.voc.com.cn/hnrb/html/2012-11/28/content_593109.htm?div=-1\" target=\"_blank\">湖南日报</a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,10466,20505],"tags":[21141,21139,12710]}